{"name":"Tactician Archetype","pages":[{"sort":100000,"name":"Tactician Archetype","type":"text","_id":"3L95FXoNWdTxyEXI","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>Hours of studying the art of warfare has allowed you to memorize countless scenarios and strategies; now is the time to support your allies by putting the theory in practice.</p><h2>@Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-archetype-feats.FwpC8VUL8NwNLlpV]{Tactician Dedication} Feat 2</h2><p><strong>Prerequisites </strong>Intelligence 14, or Wisdom 14, or Charisma 14</p><hr /><p>You become trained in Warfare Lore; if you were already trained in Warfare Lore, you become trained in a skill of your choice. You gain the @Compendium[pf2e.feats-srd.knrawm4bMbDL9XS3]{Ambush Tactics} skill feat, even if you don't meet the skill feat's requirements.</p><p>Choose a @Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-features.bZ23AYw3GMsFZdzE]{Paradigm} that corresponds to the ability you used to qualify for the archetype. You can use that ability modifier on Warfare Lore checks instead of Intelligence, and you have that paradigm for all purposes, but you donâ€™t gain any of the other abilities it grants. You become trained in tactician class DC. You can't use gambit actions.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> You cannot select another dedication feat until you have gained two other feats from the tactician archetype.</p><h2>@Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-archetype-feats.ya241bBs1K3Rs3Nk]{Basic Advice} Feat 4</h2><p><strong>Prerequisites </strong>Tactician Dedication</p><hr /><p>You gain a 1st- or 2nd-level tactician feat.</p><h2>@Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-archetype-feats.ya241bBs1K3Rs3Nk]{Brilliant Planner} Feat 4</h2><p><strong>Prerequisites</strong> Tactician Dedication</p><hr /><p>Your knowledge of warfare is peerless. You gain the @Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-features.Sc0Rb6USzcVA89ZT]{Expert Planner} class feature. At 7th level you become a master in Warfare Lore, and at 15th level, you become legendary in Warfare Lore and you become an expert in your tactician class DC.</p><h2>@Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-archetype-feats.eE7EPOzgpzwJjuKx]{Advanced Advice} Feat 6</h2><p><strong>Prerequisites </strong>Basic Advice</p><hr /><p>You gain a tactician feat. For the purpose of meeting its prerequisites, your tactician level is equal to half your character level.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> You can select this feat more than once. Each time you select it, you gain another tactician feat.</p><h2>@Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-archetype-feats.rXGOi7CkOt9I9S3o]{Latent Genius} Feat 6</h2><p><strong>Prerequisites </strong>Basic Advice</p><hr /><p>Great ideas have begun to spark in your mind. You can use gambit actions, as described in the @Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-features.ij0cO1W0JblG7auC]{Gambit} trait.</p><h2>@Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-archetype-feats.XCLKw1TVLOoLoBjC]{Tactical Awareness} Feat 10</h2><p><strong>Prerequisites</strong> Tactician Dedication</p><hr /><p>You gain the @Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-features.XtNR2HGal75XdvTz]{Tactical Awareness} class feature.</p><p></p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"G0qdvWcx08H5cMos":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"743a44c2108ca4ffb43fbe636530ebacd600a979","sourceId":"JournalEntry.zzK4aUjErwHZ0FdJ"},"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.zzK4aUjErwHZ0FdJ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1690037309381,"modifiedTime":1690691487214,"lastModifiedBy":"G0qdvWcx08H5cMos"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"vNxNOIGBF1nA70A9"}
